1. Top Directory
==
Each chapter has its own directory like intro, address, process and so on.

2. Where to Place the bugs
==
In top directory, there are files named by page number. List bugs in its page number named file.

3. Bug Report format
==
Bug id: in each file, start from 1 and increase sequence.
position: for example, 5/1 is in 1th line of 5th paragraph.
Wrong words: words or paragraph.
Corrected words: fixed words.
Reporter: who report this bug.
